<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><style>:root{--accent:#89b4fa;--border:rgba(255,255,255,.08);--text:rgba(255,255,255,.92);--subtext:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;color:var(--text);overflow:hidden;background:#000}#bg{position:fixed;inset:-10px;background-size:cover;background-position:center;filter:brightness(.3) blur(12px);z-index:0;transform:translateZ(0)}#wrap{position:relative;height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:25px;z-index:10}#header{flex-shrink:0;margin-bottom:25px;text-align:left}#title-container{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}#close{cursor:pointer;opacity:.6;display:flex}#close:hover{opacity:1}#close svg{width:22px;height:22px;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:2.5;fill:none}h1{font-size:20px;letter-spacing:.5px;font-weight:600;opacity:.9}#viewport{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;scrollbar-width:none;-ms-overflow-style:none}#viewport::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}.container{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;padding-bottom:50px}.info-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;text-align:left}.label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:10px;display:block}h2{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;color:#fff}p{font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:10px}.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-top:15px}.stat-box{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:14px;border-radius:10px}.stat-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--subtext);display:block;margin-bottom:2px}.stat-val{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#fff}footer{margin-top:10px;font-size:12px;color:var(--subtext);padding:15px 0;text-align:center;opacity:.6}</style></head><body><div id="bg"></div><div id="wrap"><div id="header"><div id="title-container"><div id="close" onclick="window.parent.postMessage('close','*')"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg></div><h1>Information</h1></div></div><div id="viewport"><div class="container"><div class="info-card"><span class="label">Organization</span><h2>HyperRush Network</h2><p>HyperRush Network is a non-profit, open-source organization focused on the development of lightweight web gaming infrastructure. We believe in a web where high-quality entertainment is accessible to everyone, regardless of hardware.</p></div><div class="info-card"><span class="label">Privacy & Analytics</span><p>To ensure network stability and monitor performance, we utilize <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>. This tool provides us with essential traffic insights without using invasive tracking cookies or collecting personally identifiable information.</p></div><div class="info-card"><span class="label">Technical Specs</span><div class="stats"><div class="stat-box"><span class="stat-label">Build</span><span class="stat-val">2026.04.Stable</span></div><div class="stat-box"><span class="stat-label">License</span><span class="stat-val">MIT Open Source</span></div><div class="stat-box"><span class="stat-label">Core</span><span class="stat-val">Virtual-Grid Engine</span></div></div></div><div class="info-card"><span class="label">Our Mission</span><p>Our goal is simple: speed. We strip away the bloat of the modern web to provide a "snappy" experience. Every component is optimized to ensure that the interface remains fluid and responsive at all times.</p></div><footer>&copy; 2026 HyperRush Network</footer></div></div></div><script>const bg=document.getElementById("bg");async function applyBackground(){const n=indexedDB.open("hrn_db",1);n.onsuccess=n=>{const e=n.target.result;if(!e.objectStoreNames.contains("background"))return;const t=e.transaction("background","readonly").objectStore("background").get("current_bg");t.onsuccess=()=>{const n=t.result?.value;n&&(bg.style.backgroundImage=`url('${n instanceof Blob?URL.createObjectURL(n):n}')`)}}}applyBackground();</script></body></html>
